data.description: This enchanting two-bedroom, one-bathroom home is nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. With its beautiful front yard boasting a play area carved out at the bottom of the property, you'll fall in love with the natural beauty that surrounds this picturesque property. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a tastefully updated kitchen and living room, where modern amenities seamlessly blend with timeless charm, creating an inviting space for gatherings and entertaining. The basement has potential to be finished for additional space! Walking distance to Lake Mahopac (home has lake rights), Volz Park with hiking trails and restaurants nearby. *Flat area in front yard near trampoline is part of this property! *New septic currently being installed! *As is sale!
